features: 【Large Capacity】Antigo shoe rack occupies a small space but provides plenty of storage space, allowing to store 20-24 pairs adult shoes. This vertical shoe rack is not only suitable for shoes but also for bags, toys, towels, sundries, books, plants, and small accessories. The tall shoe rack comes with an additional hook, you can hang keys, umbrellas, bags, etc., very practical design.

【Sturdy and Durable Structure】The narrow shoe rack is made of 13mm thickened corrosion-resistant metal pipes, upgraded strengthened pp connectors, and high-quality Pp Gaskets, which enhance the stability, increase the load capacity up to 50 LB and improve the corner shoe rack lasting life. Say goodbye to the flimsy and cheap shoe rack for closet small space.

【Save Space Unique Design】The shoe rack for entryway is with a small size 17.1"L x 11.8"W x 78.7"H, effectively utilize the vertical space. And 10 tier shoe rack organizer can be split into 2 unites 5 tier shoe organizer to meet different storage needs. It fits all the size of space, such as entryway, closet, living room, hallways, cloakroom, bedroom, garage, etc. Keep shoes always neat and tidy.

【Suitable for All Types Shoes】This shoe shelf fits all kinds of shoes, not only slippers, flat shoes,sandals,but also boots, high heels and so on. You can remove the one or some layers to store high boots. Additional 2 PP Gaskets avoid falling from the gap of steel pipes when you store objects such as the narrow heel of high heels.

【Easy to Assemble】The free standing shoe racks comes with brief assembling instruction, it is easy to install, no screw is required. An additioanl disposable small hammer help save labor,make the organizador de zapatos easier to be set up abd stabler.

【Worry-Free Service】Please refer to the shoe stand installation manual and ensure all the parts are included before installing. If you have any problems with the metal shoe rack, please feel free to contact us. We replace or refund any defective products within 1 year after purchase.

【Warm Tips】When installing the shoe racks for bedroom closet, please make sure that all parts are tightly pressed without leaving any space. And it would be more steadier if you put the heavy objects at the bottom layer.

Warming Tips： Please check whether the accessories are complete according to the manual before installation. Don't touch the cut surface of the steel tube. Please rotate the pipe slowly into the connector instead of inserting the pipe directly in. Please use the hammer to make sure that all parts are tightly pressed. And it would be more steadier if you put the heavy objects at the bottom layer. Keep out of the sun to prevent the fabric from deteriorating and to prolong its life. If the plastic connector inlet is too tight, try immersing the plastic connector in hot water for a while.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great shoe rack
reviews.reviewText: Extra capacity shoe rack that was easy to install. Love that I was able to store almost 30 pairs of shoes on this fairly light weight but durable rack. Although not necessary, I felt more comfortable anchoring it. I also purchased one for my daughter and she likes it as much as I do.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Space saving, price is ok
reviews.reviewText: Light weight so put something heavy on bottom to anchor it. Created more storage space in a small walk in closet. I can now use the opened space to store other things. I am retired and live in a wonderful retirement community, however storage space is minimal so this is/was important. Plus my shoes are now visible and easier to access, so they all get in rotation to wear. Just swap around as seasons change.
